ca.keefer.sanemethod
Class Constants

java.lang.Object
  ca.keefer.sanemethod.Constants

public class Constants
extends java.lang.Object

This class contains configurable constants for a number of internal functions, including game states, control bindings, and tile/sprite sizes. It is entirely static.

Version:
1.3
Author:
Christopher Keefer
